thread.title: Debra
thread.title_full: SecurCare Self Storage reviewed by Debra

author: Debra
title: Debra
text: I am happy with my small storage unit and it is on the ground floor, which was one of my requirements. The only thing that kept me from giving the company 5 stars is the fact that there are no small units that you can drive up to. The smaller units seem to be inside and down a hallway. It is not bad, and the halls are very well lit. Thank you.
